ion paper demonstrates this approach in real-world\napplication scenarios for machine vision and robotics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 22:17:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Oct 2022 15:47:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-11"}
