alue of the Davenport\nConstant $\\mathsf D(G)$ for finite abelian $p$-groups, a streamlined proof of\nthe Kemnitz Conjecture, and the resolution of a problem of Xiaoyu He regarding\nzero-sums of length $k\\exp(G)$ related to a conjecture of Kubertin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 23:28:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
